SHORT_DESCR.P: County Council established a provider list, using a Dynamic Purchasing System (DPS), of organisations able to provide transport services including local bus, mainstream home-to-school, school meals transport, special education needs, high dependency, adult social care and curriculum transport services.

The purpose of this tender is to establish the Dynamic Purchasing System agreement between the County Council and service provider(s) for the provision of transport services. Under this agreement, transport will be provided using vehicles of various capacities (minimum four seats and upwards and in accordance with current Public Service Vehicle (PSV) Legislation, Private Hire or Hackney Carriage legislation or under Section 19 or 22 Permit)
